=========================================== QUERY/Commands========================================
1. Create Database 
	create database databaseName;

2. Use the Database 
	use databaseName;

3. Create Table

		create table tableName(colName datatype(size) , ....);
Data type: int , varchar, char, decimal, date , ....

4. Insert data to the table :
	insert into tableName(colName,...) values(val1, ...);

5. Fetch data from the table

	It will fetch all the data from the table
	select * from tableName; 

	To fetch specific columns
	select col1, col2, .. from tableName;


